OL,3,CBelgium's 'slippery slope' for
OL,4,Cassisted dying laws could provide
OL,5,Cexample for UK
OL,7,FOver the past 20 years about a dozen
OL,8,Fcountries around the world have
OL,9,Fadopted Assisted Dying, or euthanasia,
OL,10,Fproviding some valuable lessons for
OL,11,FMPs in England and Wales, ITV News'
OL,12,FEurope Editor James Mates reports
OL,14,FThe debate on assisted dying in
OL,15,FBelgium is more than 20 years ahead of
OL,16,Fthe UK, so much so that even doctor-
OL,17,Fassisted suicide is far from unknown.
