OL,7,FSince euthanasia, as they refer to it,
OL,8,Fwas introduced in 2002, it has also
OL,9,Fbeen extended to cover under-18s in
OL,10,Fexceptional circumstances, with
OL,11,Fterminal illness and their parents'
OL,12,Fconsent.
OL,14,FThe Belgian example looks like a
OL,15,Fclassic 'slippery slope' a well-
OL,16,Fintentioned law being stretched and
OL,17,Fexpanded way beyond the intentions of
OL,18,Fthe original framers.
