OL,7,FMany Belgians accept that is what has
OL,8,Fhappened, but by and large, they are
OL,9,Fhappy that things have worked out this
OL,10,Fway.
OL,12,FIndeed a mainstream opposition party,
OL,13,FOpen VLD, are pushing for legislation
OL,14,Fto make the law even more flexible,
OL,15,Fespecially for those suffering from
OL,16,Fdementia. "We start from the liberal
OL,17,Fprinciple that you decide for yourself
OL,18,Fabout your life," they say.
