OL,7,FCurrently, a patient can elect to die
OL,8,Fwith a doctor's help if they are
OL,9,Fterminally ill, in sustained and long-
OL,10,Flasting pain, or suffering from
OL,11,Fmultiple debilities of extreme old
OL,12,Fage. Last year more than 3,400 people
OL,13,Fchose this route, more than any
OL,14,Fcountry in Europe except the
OL,15,FNetherlands.
