OL,7,FIt is the 'long-term pain condition'
OL,8,Fthat has proved most controversial
OL,9,Fbecause it also covers those suffering
OL,10,Ffrom extreme mental pain - such as
OL,11,Fchronic depression ` even if the
OL,12,Fpatient is physically healthy.
OL,14,FWe spent an evening with Dirk and
OL,15,FKarin Vervaet whose daughter Elien
OL,16,Fdied by euthanasia last year. She was
OL,17,Fonly 24.
