OL,7,FWhatever one's view of this
OL,8,Fheartbreaking story, it goes way
OL,9,Fbeyond anything envisaged in the
OL,10,FAssisted Dying Bill currently before
OL,11,FParliament.
OL,13,FThat strictly limits its use to those
OL,14,Fwho are terminally ill with less than
OL,15,Fsix months to live. But if the Bill
OL,16,Feventually becomes law, could such
OL,17,Flimits ever hold?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
