OL,7,F"I know elderly people who, on only
OL,8,Fabout their third day in hospital,
OL,9,Fhave been asked 'did you already think
OL,10,Fabout the possibility of euthanasia?'
OL,11,Fand they found that very upsetting".
OL,13,FThose who worry that pressure on
OL,14,Fhealth budgets and hospital beds,
OL,15,Fpressure from families, or simply
OL,16,Fembarrassment at being a burden may be
OL,17,Fpushing people into choosing to die,
OL,18,Fare a minority in Belgium. The public
OL,19,Fmood here is firmly that the relief of
OL,20,Fsuffering outweighs other
OL,21,Fconsiderations.
