OL,7,FBut the lesson from the Belgian
OL,8,Fexperience is that once the taboo has
OL,9,Fbeen broken the scope and extent of
OL,10,Fassisted dying will, over time,
OL,11,Finevitably expand. And whether or not
OL,12,Fone thinks that would be a good thing,
OL,13,Fone should be aware of that before
OL,14,Ftaking the first step.
